Enum ColunasSalas

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ColunasSalas>
es_grupoL.AppGestaoHorarios.ColunasSalas
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ColunasSalas>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum ColunasSalas extends Enum<ColunasSalas>
Enum representing the columns of a file containing information about classrooms. It provides methods to retrieve information about classrooms based on specific criteria. Each constant represents a specific column in the classrooms data.
Version:
1.1
